4:54 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "#"
5:2 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# `write_text` truncates (or creates) the file; `append_text` appends"
6:70 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# to the end (creating the file if it does not exist)."
